WEBVTT

STYLE
::cue {
font-size: 1em;
font-weight: bold;
color: #ffffff;
}

00:01:31.180 --> 00:01:34.700 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:01:34.820 --> 00:01:37.740 line:80%
=Episode 2=

00:01:54.060 --> 00:01:55.340 line:80%
My Fengfu acupoint is sealed.

00:01:56.620 --> 00:01:57.540 line:80%
I can't move.

00:02:03.130 --> 00:02:04.070 line:80%
Your poison flared up?

00:02:04.570 --> 00:02:05.410 line:80%
No.

00:02:10.020 --> 00:02:11.090 line:80%
Are you afraid of the dark?

00:02:13.430 --> 00:02:14.280 line:80%
Don't be.

00:02:14.300 --> 00:02:15.140 line:80%
I'm not afraid.

00:02:16.780 --> 00:02:17.620 line:80%
This is a box.

00:02:18.650 --> 00:02:19.680 line:80%
They didn't harm us

00:02:19.680 --> 00:02:20.720 line:80%
while we were unconscious.

00:02:20.760 --> 00:02:22.300 line:80%
They probably want to capture us alive.

00:02:22.300 --> 00:02:23.210 line:80%
Who are they?

00:02:23.516 --> 00:02:24.836 line:80%
Why do they want to capture you?

00:02:25.180 --> 00:02:26.620 line:80%
Shouldn't that be asked to you?

00:02:27.413 --> 00:02:28.837 line:80%
Those who can reach Qingque Sect

00:02:29.485 --> 00:02:30.609 line:80%
should be from the Six Sects.

00:02:35.460 --> 00:02:36.300 line:80%
Ning,

00:02:36.973 --> 00:02:37.970 line:80%
turn your head a little.

00:02:38.740 --> 00:02:39.580 line:80%
What?

00:02:41.140 --> 00:02:41.990 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:02:42.020 --> 00:02:42.953 line:80%
Releasing your acupoint.

00:02:46.490 --> 00:02:47.410 line:80%
I'll count to three.

00:02:48.140 --> 00:02:49.180 line:80%
We'll rush out together.

00:02:49.300 --> 00:02:50.140 line:80%
Okay.

00:02:50.250 --> 00:02:51.090 line:80%
One,

00:02:51.780 --> 00:02:52.620 line:80%
two,

00:02:52.690 --> 00:02:53.530 line:80%
three.

00:03:08.020 --> 00:03:08.860 line:80%
Careful.

00:03:29.340 --> 00:03:30.410 line:80%
Chang Ning!

00:03:39.530 --> 00:03:40.530 line:80%
Let go,

00:03:40.690 --> 00:03:41.930 line:80%
or we'll all die.

00:03:42.780 --> 00:03:44.580 line:80%
Halfway is the worst way,

00:03:44.711 --> 00:03:45.860 line:80%
especially when saving lives.

00:03:48.860 --> 00:03:49.900 line:80%
Help!

00:03:50.090 --> 00:03:51.650 line:80%
Master!

00:03:52.410 --> 00:03:53.460 line:80%
If no one comes,

00:03:53.900 --> 00:03:55.250 line:80%
we'll die!

00:04:04.250 --> 00:04:06.250 line:80%
Zhao, hold the rope!

00:04:22.780 --> 00:04:23.620 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:24.170 --> 00:04:25.010 line:80%
what happened?

00:04:26.696 --> 00:04:28.066 line:80%
Someone is trying to capture Ning.

00:04:29.290 --> 00:04:30.130 line:80%
Chang.

00:04:31.460 --> 00:04:32.300 line:80%
Chang Ning.

00:04:45.530 --> 00:04:46.370 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:04:46.530 --> 00:04:47.370 line:80%
He's fine.

00:04:47.900 --> 00:04:48.740 line:80%
He'll wake up soon.

00:04:49.550 --> 00:04:50.400 line:80%
Zhao,

00:04:50.410 --> 00:04:51.410 line:80%
are your hands okay?

00:04:52.170 --> 00:04:53.010 line:80%
I'm fine.

00:04:53.700 --> 00:04:55.940 line:80%
Xingjia got anxious
and wrapped extra rounds.

00:04:56.460 --> 00:04:57.530 line:80%
It's all my fault.

00:04:57.850 --> 00:04:58.780 line:80%
I failed to protect you.

00:05:00.050 --> 00:05:01.050 line:80%
The villains are bold.

00:05:01.730 --> 00:05:02.580 line:80%
Not your fault.

00:05:04.340 --> 00:05:05.180 line:80%
But Master,

00:05:05.530 --> 00:05:07.410 line:80%
how did the people in black get here?

00:05:07.460 --> 00:05:08.970 line:80%
Even flying birds can't do that.

00:05:09.730 --> 00:05:11.290 line:80%
Could this be the same people

00:05:11.460 --> 00:05:13.010 line:80%
who massacred Chang Fort?

00:05:14.090 --> 00:05:16.380 line:80%
The Jianghu has been peaceful for years.

00:05:16.820 --> 00:05:18.020 line:80%
We let our guard down.

00:05:18.610 --> 00:05:19.460 line:80%
Now,

00:05:19.650 --> 00:05:21.580 line:80%
we must stay alert.

00:05:25.940 --> 00:05:26.780 line:80%
Yunke,

00:05:26.940 --> 00:05:27.850 line:80%
I found several bodies

00:05:28.020 --> 00:05:29.340 line:80%
in Qingque Town.

00:05:30.020 --> 00:05:31.850 line:80%
The culprit disguised themselves

00:05:32.090 --> 00:05:33.110 line:80%
as Guangtian Sect guards.

00:05:34.380 --> 00:05:35.220 line:80%
Master,

00:05:35.410 --> 00:05:36.410 line:80%
it's my fault.

00:05:37.020 --> 00:05:38.580 line:80%
I'll go to pursue the culprit.

00:05:39.290 --> 00:05:40.516 line:80%
They first massacred Chang Fort

00:05:41.530 --> 00:05:43.900 line:80%
and then barged in here to silence Ning.

00:05:43.900 --> 00:05:45.186 line:80%
This can only be the demon sect.

00:05:46.050 --> 00:05:47.900 line:80%
The Patriarch's ritual is imminent.

00:05:48.050 --> 00:05:49.410 line:80%
We can't have another riot.

00:05:50.260 --> 00:05:51.100 line:80%
From today,

00:05:51.380 --> 00:05:54.340 line:80%
strengthen the internal
and external gates' guard.

00:05:54.786 --> 00:05:55.970 line:80%
Everyone going up the mountain

00:05:56.090 --> 00:05:56.970 line:80%
must be checked.

00:05:57.290 --> 00:05:58.130 line:80%
No negligence.

00:05:58.380 --> 00:05:59.220 line:80%
- Yes.
- Yes.

00:06:07.020 --> 00:06:07.860 line:80%
Zhao.

00:06:09.020 --> 00:06:10.380 line:80%
The Siqi Sect is too weak.

00:06:10.460 --> 00:06:11.750 line:80%
She couldn't even stand one move.

00:06:12.020 --> 00:06:12.889 line:80%
My foundation is weak.

00:06:12.900 --> 00:06:14.269 line:80%
It has nothing to do with the sect.

00:06:14.340 --> 00:06:15.180 line:80%
Xiaolan,

00:06:15.227 --> 00:06:17.040 line:80%
you didn't eat breakfast
this morning, right?

00:06:17.253 --> 00:06:18.700 line:80%
So, you don't have enough strength.

00:06:18.850 --> 00:06:19.690 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:06:20.170 --> 00:06:21.610 line:80%
I'll take Xiaolan to find some food.

00:06:22.090 --> 00:06:22.930 line:80%
Let's go.

00:06:23.090 --> 00:06:23.930 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:06:25.380 --> 00:06:27.460 line:80%
it seems your hand has healed.

00:06:30.090 --> 00:06:30.930 line:80%
Yes.

00:06:31.850 --> 00:06:32.850 line:80%
Thanks for your concern.

00:06:33.260 --> 00:06:34.100 line:80%
Let's go.

00:06:34.530 --> 00:06:35.380 line:80%
Zhuo!

00:06:47.500 --> 00:06:48.560 line:80%
(Ding Zhuo)
I'm Ding Zhuo.

00:06:48.573 --> 00:06:50.730 line:80%
Channeling inner power
into the weapon.

00:06:50.820 --> 00:06:51.700 line:80%
So powerful.

00:06:52.020 --> 00:06:53.140 line:80%
This is Zhuo.

00:06:53.460 --> 00:06:54.673 line:80%
He just emerged from seclusion.

00:06:54.780 --> 00:06:55.620 line:80%
Cai Zhao.

00:06:56.290 --> 00:06:57.130 line:80%
Hi, Zhuo.

00:06:57.130 --> 00:06:58.000 line:80%
Zhuo.

00:07:01.290 --> 00:07:02.130 line:80%
May I spar with you?

00:07:04.900 --> 00:07:05.740 line:80%
Zhao,

00:07:06.020 --> 00:07:07.820 line:80%
Zhuo is obsessed with martial arts.

00:07:07.850 --> 00:07:08.700 line:80%
Whenever he spars,

00:07:08.700 --> 00:07:10.340 line:80%
he fights until one can't stand.

00:07:10.970 --> 00:07:11.940 line:80%
Don't spar with him.

00:07:12.580 --> 00:07:13.420 line:80%
What?

00:07:14.730 --> 00:07:15.570 line:80%
Are you afraid?

00:07:16.940 --> 00:07:17.780 line:80%
Sure. Let's spar.

00:07:19.260 --> 00:07:20.100 line:80%
I'm ready.

00:07:23.500 --> 00:07:24.340 line:80%
Zhuo,

00:07:24.410 --> 00:07:25.250 line:80%
you've lost.

00:07:28.260 --> 00:07:29.460 line:80%
Cai Zhao, you cheated.

00:07:29.700 --> 00:07:31.290 line:80%
Lingbo, you can't wrong me.

00:07:32.290 --> 00:07:33.460 line:80%
I didn't use hidden weapons

00:07:33.780 --> 00:07:34.820 line:80%
or attack from behind.

00:07:35.380 --> 00:07:36.220 line:80%
How did I cheat?

00:07:36.340 --> 00:07:37.900 line:80%
But it hasn't even started.

00:07:38.260 --> 00:07:39.850 line:80%
Martial contests are fatal struggles.

00:07:39.850 --> 00:07:40.706 line:80%
At a critical moment,

00:07:40.717 --> 00:07:42.090 line:80%
do we need to bathe, burn incense,

00:07:42.090 --> 00:07:43.530 line:80%
and beat drums before starting?

00:07:44.020 --> 00:07:46.140 line:80%
No wonder I was ambushed
a few days ago.

00:07:46.380 --> 00:07:47.900 line:80%
It must have been because everyone

00:07:47.900 --> 00:07:49.050 line:80%
weren't prepared.

00:07:49.050 --> 00:07:49.890 line:80%
I...

00:07:53.260 --> 00:07:54.140 line:80%
I admit defeat.

00:07:55.140 --> 00:07:55.980 line:80%
Zhuo...

00:07:56.340 --> 00:07:57.740 line:80%
Thank you, Zhuo.

00:07:59.340 --> 00:08:00.180 line:80%
Xiaolan.

00:08:03.380 --> 00:08:04.220 line:80%
Cai Zhao,

00:08:05.020 --> 00:08:06.050 line:80%
just you wait.

00:08:08.900 --> 00:08:12.493 line:80%
(Double Lotus Palace)

00:08:12.504 --> 00:08:14.537 line:80%
It's said that the previous lord,
Yin Dai, had only

00:08:16.260 --> 00:08:17.970 line:80%
two daughters, Qinglian and Sulian.

00:08:18.780 --> 00:08:19.780 line:80%
Thus, it's named

00:08:20.410 --> 00:08:21.730 line:80%
Double Lotus Palace.

00:08:22.530 --> 00:08:24.020 line:80%
Though it lacks grandeur,

00:08:24.700 --> 00:08:25.970 line:80%
it is elegant and extraordinary,

00:08:26.340 --> 00:08:27.410 line:80%
stunningly beautiful.

00:08:30.170 --> 00:08:31.210 line:80%
The tiles are fragile,

00:08:31.410 --> 00:08:33.290 line:80%
transported from the Western Regions

00:08:33.810 --> 00:08:34.860 line:80%
without damage.

00:08:36.100 --> 00:08:37.140 line:80%
Truly priceless.

00:08:38.493 --> 00:08:39.740 line:80%
Qingque Sect has always valued

00:08:39.740 --> 00:08:40.620 line:80%
strict cultivation

00:08:41.260 --> 00:08:43.100 line:80%
and simple living.

00:08:44.380 --> 00:08:46.930 line:80%
Lord Yin managed such a palace,

00:08:46.930 --> 00:08:47.900 line:80%
truly a model

00:08:48.740 --> 00:08:50.050 line:80%
of household management.

00:08:52.180 --> 00:08:54.220 line:80%
(Lotus and Moon)

00:09:07.410 --> 00:09:09.260 line:80%
You two faced danger.

00:09:09.620 --> 00:09:11.290 line:80%
I wanted to visit,

00:09:12.050 --> 00:09:13.220 line:80%
but the sect was busy

00:09:13.220 --> 00:09:14.450 line:80%
reorganizing defenses,

00:09:14.450 --> 00:09:15.500 line:80%
checking disciples.

00:09:16.020 --> 00:09:17.380 line:80%
I didn't have time.

00:09:17.930 --> 00:09:19.570 line:80%
Today, I finally has a chance.

00:09:19.900 --> 00:09:22.290 line:80%
This gift is a token of care

00:09:22.620 --> 00:09:23.780 line:80%
to calm your nerves.

00:09:25.170 --> 00:09:26.220 line:80%
Thank you for your concern.

00:09:26.930 --> 00:09:28.650 line:80%
But we've done nothing.

00:09:29.170 --> 00:09:30.260 line:80%
A gift is not needed.

00:09:39.140 --> 00:09:41.680 line:80%
Your aunt and I bought this bracelet

00:09:41.690 --> 00:09:43.570 line:80%
when traveling Jianghu.

00:09:43.650 --> 00:09:45.260 line:80%
You can take it, right?

00:09:49.380 --> 00:09:50.260 line:80%
Thank you, Lady Yin.

00:09:56.020 --> 00:09:56.860 line:80%
Lingbo,

00:09:58.330 --> 00:10:01.290 line:80%
Ms. Cai and I were like sisters.

00:10:01.530 --> 00:10:03.050 line:80%
You and Zhao are fellow disciples.

00:10:03.900 --> 00:10:06.290 line:80%
You should treat her well.

00:10:06.650 --> 00:10:08.140 line:80%
It's hard to have such connections.

00:10:08.650 --> 00:10:09.490 line:80%
Yes,

00:10:09.860 --> 00:10:10.780 line:80%
Mother.

00:10:21.900 --> 00:10:22.780 line:80%
Ning,

00:10:23.620 --> 00:10:25.450 line:80%
I know your family has fine collections.

00:10:25.810 --> 00:10:28.100 line:80%
Ordinary items might not impress you.

00:10:28.740 --> 00:10:29.650 line:80%
Nanny Mao.

00:10:29.820 --> 00:10:30.670 line:80%
Yes.

00:10:30.690 --> 00:10:31.570 line:80%
Take Ning

00:10:31.570 --> 00:10:33.410 line:80%
to the Treasure Vault

00:10:33.860 --> 00:10:35.260 line:80%
and see if he likes anything.

00:10:35.620 --> 00:10:36.460 line:80%
Yes.

00:10:57.740 --> 00:10:58.940 line:80%
Have some tea.

00:11:00.170 --> 00:11:01.330 line:80%
Thank you, Lady Yin.

00:11:18.980 --> 00:11:20.940 line:80%
You have good taste.

00:11:21.450 --> 00:11:23.330 line:80%
This jade was soaked in phoenix blood,

00:11:23.650 --> 00:11:24.860 line:80%
extremely nourishing

00:11:25.140 --> 00:11:26.170 line:80%
and precious.

00:11:26.980 --> 00:11:27.900 line:80%
If you like it,

00:11:28.450 --> 00:11:29.860 line:80%
you may take it.

00:11:32.170 --> 00:11:33.010 line:80%
Madam,

00:11:33.860 --> 00:11:35.290 line:80%
this was my family's property.

00:11:35.740 --> 00:11:37.650 line:80%
I just want to bring it back.

00:11:39.140 --> 00:11:39.980 line:80%
Mr. Chang,

00:11:40.220 --> 00:11:41.930 line:80%
this is a treasured item of Madam.

00:11:41.930 --> 00:11:42.980 line:80%
She can give it to you.

00:11:43.170 --> 00:11:44.530 line:80%
How can it be taken back?

00:11:47.500 --> 00:11:48.410 line:80%
Three years ago,

00:11:49.220 --> 00:11:50.860 line:80%
my father fell ill

00:11:51.170 --> 00:11:52.083 line:80%
due to Ms. Cai's death.

00:11:52.380 --> 00:11:54.740 line:80%
Lord Qi let my father recuperate here.

00:11:55.290 --> 00:11:56.130 line:80%
So,

00:11:56.330 --> 00:11:58.020 line:80%
my father gave him this blood jade,

00:11:59.450 --> 00:12:01.900 line:80%
but he overheard a quarrel
between you two.

00:12:03.020 --> 00:12:04.020 line:80%
You said

00:12:04.450 --> 00:12:06.690 line:80%
Cai Pingshu sacrificed herself
for the world,

00:12:06.860 --> 00:12:07.900 line:80%
fighting Nie Hengcheng

00:12:07.900 --> 00:12:09.260 line:80%
to mutual ruin.

00:12:10.429 --> 00:12:11.603 line:80%
But that wretch dragged it out

00:12:12.050 --> 00:12:13.930 line:80%
for over ten years before dying,

00:12:14.690 --> 00:12:15.810 line:80%
truly detestable.

00:12:17.570 --> 00:12:18.810 line:80%
My father was enraged,

00:12:18.980 --> 00:12:20.380 line:80%
so he left here in sickness.

00:12:20.860 --> 00:12:21.900 line:80%
Every time he recalled it,

00:12:23.220 --> 00:12:24.260 line:80%
he was heartbroken.

00:12:24.900 --> 00:12:25.740 line:80%
Chang Ning,

00:12:26.140 --> 00:12:27.810 line:80%
we kindly took you in,

00:12:27.980 --> 00:12:29.380 line:80%
yet you disobeyed.

00:12:29.380 --> 00:12:30.650 line:80%
Now, you even slander my mother.

00:12:30.810 --> 00:12:31.860 line:80%
Madam knows

00:12:33.100 --> 00:12:34.500 line:80%
whether she had said that.

00:12:35.140 --> 00:12:35.980 line:80%
Lady Yin,

00:12:37.410 --> 00:12:38.250 line:80%
is this true?

00:12:40.380 --> 00:12:41.620 line:80%
Of course not.

00:12:42.020 --> 00:12:43.380 line:80%
Your family is despicable.

00:12:43.740 --> 00:12:46.020 line:80%
You even drew thieves here.

00:12:46.530 --> 00:12:47.860 line:80%
As a martial family,

00:12:48.039 --> 00:12:49.388 line:80%
you collected wealth everywhere.

00:12:49.500 --> 00:12:51.260 line:80%
Who knows what you hid

00:12:51.260 --> 00:12:52.530 line:80%
to provoke the massacre?

00:12:52.980 --> 00:12:54.170 line:80%
My father was fond of wealth

00:12:54.500 --> 00:12:55.650 line:80%
but fair.

00:12:56.220 --> 00:12:57.260 line:80%
He owed no one.

00:12:57.930 --> 00:12:58.980 line:80%
The Yin family was greedy

00:12:59.277 --> 00:13:00.323 line:80%
for wealth and reputation,

00:13:00.930 --> 00:13:03.290 line:80%
which caused Ms. Cai's early death.

00:13:06.380 --> 00:13:08.450 line:80%
Ning, you're slandering us.

00:13:08.860 --> 00:13:10.220 line:80%
How disrespectful

00:13:10.220 --> 00:13:11.260 line:80%
and impolite.

00:13:11.650 --> 00:13:13.100 line:80%
Today, I'll teach you a lesson

00:13:13.100 --> 00:13:14.900 line:80%
on behalf of the Lord.

00:13:15.620 --> 00:13:16.750 line:80%
- Nanny Mao.
- Yes.

00:13:16.780 --> 00:13:17.620 line:80%
Madam,

00:13:18.140 --> 00:13:19.930 line:80%
Lingbo already lectured me

00:13:20.290 --> 00:13:21.570 line:80%
openly and secretly.

00:13:22.500 --> 00:13:23.340 line:80%
Could this be

00:13:24.380 --> 00:13:25.570 line:80%
your instruction?

00:13:26.780 --> 00:13:27.930 line:80%
Is today's kindness

00:13:28.220 --> 00:13:29.500 line:80%
to win over Zhao,

00:13:29.860 --> 00:13:31.980 line:80%
whom Lord Qi values,

00:13:32.220 --> 00:13:33.690 line:80%
or out of guilt

00:13:34.450 --> 00:13:35.530 line:80%
for Ms. Cai Pingshu?

00:13:35.810 --> 00:13:36.900 line:80%
Nonsense.

00:13:36.970 --> 00:13:37.830 line:80%
Guards!

00:13:37.840 --> 00:13:38.680 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:39.300 --> 00:13:40.140 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:13:40.140 --> 00:13:41.140 line:80%
Seize Chang Ning.

00:13:41.360 --> 00:13:42.230 line:80%
Yes.

00:13:42.260 --> 00:13:43.700 line:80%
- You...
- Stop.

00:13:52.650 --> 00:13:53.490 line:80%
Nanny Mao,

00:13:54.170 --> 00:13:55.030 line:80%
what is this about?

00:13:55.050 --> 00:13:55.890 line:80%
Milord.

00:13:55.980 --> 00:13:57.480 line:80%
Father, Chang Ning...

00:14:04.380 --> 00:14:05.220 line:80%
Dear,

00:14:06.380 --> 00:14:08.170 line:80%
Ning is my guest.

00:14:08.980 --> 00:14:09.820 line:80%
Besides,

00:14:10.170 --> 00:14:11.290 line:80%
he is young,

00:14:11.650 --> 00:14:12.860 line:80%
facing so much turmoil,

00:14:13.260 --> 00:14:15.780 line:80%
so his emotions fluctuate.

00:14:16.450 --> 00:14:17.290 line:80%
As an elder,

00:14:18.140 --> 00:14:19.780 line:80%
you should show more tolerance.

00:14:24.170 --> 00:14:25.010 line:80%
Ning,

00:14:25.810 --> 00:14:26.836 line:80%
your wounds aren't healed.

00:14:27.100 --> 00:14:28.170 line:80%
Go back

00:14:28.650 --> 00:14:29.930 line:80%
and rest properly.

00:14:44.650 --> 00:14:45.770 line:80%
- Master.
- Zhao.

00:14:46.900 --> 00:14:47.740 line:80%
Come with me.

00:15:06.050 --> 00:15:06.890 line:80%
Master,

00:15:07.050 --> 00:15:08.260 line:80%
is what Chang Ning said true?

00:15:13.130 --> 00:15:14.570 line:80%
Aunt went to kill Nie Hengcheng.

00:15:14.670 --> 00:15:15.900 line:80%
What does that have to do

00:15:15.900 --> 00:15:17.170 line:80%
with Lord Yin Dai?

00:15:22.912 --> 00:15:24.059 line:80%
This is the Withered Branch.

00:15:24.980 --> 00:15:26.380 line:80%
Your aunt brought it here.

00:15:30.900 --> 00:15:32.020 line:80%
Withered Branch?

00:15:32.860 --> 00:15:33.866 line:80%
I thought it was extinct.

00:15:34.413 --> 00:15:35.650 line:80%
I came from a humble background.

00:15:36.220 --> 00:15:37.060 line:80%
Back then,

00:15:37.260 --> 00:15:38.290 line:80%
I was just

00:15:38.290 --> 00:15:40.050 line:80%
an unremarkable outer disciple,

00:15:40.690 --> 00:15:42.980 line:80%
often bullied by senior brothers.

00:15:53.700 --> 00:15:56.980 line:80%
(Young Qi Yunke, Qingque Sect)

00:15:57.860 --> 00:16:00.100 line:80%
Until that day, Pingshu appeared

00:16:00.810 --> 00:16:01.930 line:80%
and rescued me.

00:16:02.900 --> 00:16:03.980 line:80%
Pingshu told me

00:16:04.500 --> 00:16:05.926 line:80%
that I have the Tianhuo Dragon Bone,

00:16:06.356 --> 00:16:07.410 line:80%
that once I break through,

00:16:07.410 --> 00:16:08.780 line:80%
I can soar,

00:16:09.620 --> 00:16:12.050 line:80%
and that I must not give up

00:16:12.113 --> 00:16:13.099 line:80%
because of early failure.

00:16:22.500 --> 00:16:24.140 line:80%
Under her guidance,

00:16:24.930 --> 00:16:26.690 line:80%
I got the Tianhuo Dragon Meridian,

00:16:27.140 --> 00:16:27.980 line:80%
becoming a disciple

00:16:28.330 --> 00:16:29.780 line:80%
of Lord Yin.

00:16:30.900 --> 00:16:32.380 line:80%
To strengthen my inner power,

00:16:32.740 --> 00:16:34.260 line:80%
she found the Withered Branch.

00:16:34.980 --> 00:16:36.020 line:80%
Once it blooms,

00:16:36.377 --> 00:16:37.397 line:80%
it can be used as medicine

00:16:38.220 --> 00:16:40.170 line:80%
to aid my cultivation.

00:16:45.450 --> 00:16:47.220 line:80%
But before it bloomed,

00:16:48.170 --> 00:16:49.740 line:80%
Nie Hengcheng

00:16:49.900 --> 00:16:51.260 line:80%
completed his dark arts,

00:16:51.500 --> 00:16:54.140 line:80%
devastating the Six Sects,

00:16:54.220 --> 00:16:55.260 line:80%
and killing countless.

00:16:59.220 --> 00:17:00.650 line:80%
I should have realized.

00:17:01.690 --> 00:17:03.980 line:80%
Pingshu was always ahead of us,

00:17:05.020 --> 00:17:06.130 line:80%
never letting us

00:17:06.290 --> 00:17:07.530 line:80%
die with her.

00:17:12.500 --> 00:17:14.180 line:80%
Whenever I think of my aunt

00:17:14.420 --> 00:17:15.700 line:80%
covered in blood,

00:17:16.500 --> 00:17:18.220 line:80%
barely alive,

00:17:20.090 --> 00:17:21.740 line:80%
I feel anger and sorrow.

00:17:24.780 --> 00:17:25.890 line:80%
If only someone had been

00:17:26.890 --> 00:17:28.220 line:80%
with her at the time,

00:17:29.890 --> 00:17:32.610 line:80%
even just to assist.

00:17:35.460 --> 00:17:36.890 line:80%
This is Jianghu:

00:17:38.610 --> 00:17:39.700 line:80%
Heroic ones

00:17:40.530 --> 00:17:41.700 line:80%
risk their lives,

00:17:43.500 --> 00:17:45.020 line:80%
yet good endings are not guaranteed.

00:17:57.940 --> 00:17:59.330 line:80%
I've long stopped

00:18:00.500 --> 00:18:01.500 line:80%
believing in karma.

00:18:05.530 --> 00:18:07.330 line:80%
That's why I said I don't like Jianghu.

00:18:07.490 --> 00:18:09.050 line:80%
Yet you and my parents insisted I come.

00:18:14.290 --> 00:18:15.700 line:80%
You don't need to enter Jianghu,

00:18:17.530 --> 00:18:18.850 line:80%
but you must become powerful.

00:18:19.810 --> 00:18:20.650 line:80%
Only then

00:18:20.780 --> 00:18:21.940 line:80%
can you live without worry.

00:18:24.370 --> 00:18:26.050 line:80%
Your aunt wanted you to learn from me

00:18:26.530 --> 00:18:27.660 line:80%
because she wanted you

00:18:27.940 --> 00:18:29.890 line:80%
to diligently practice

00:18:30.166 --> 00:18:31.386 line:80%
and refine your martial skills.

00:18:32.370 --> 00:18:33.370 line:80%
In life,

00:18:33.980 --> 00:18:36.460 line:80%
there are times beyond one's control.

00:18:36.850 --> 00:18:38.530 line:80%
Only by becoming strong

00:18:39.180 --> 00:18:40.180 line:80%
can one be free.

00:18:41.610 --> 00:18:42.450 line:80%
Back then,

00:18:42.810 --> 00:18:44.050 line:80%
no matter what others said,

00:18:44.660 --> 00:18:47.130 line:80%
your aunt acted as she wished.

00:18:49.740 --> 00:18:50.700 line:80%
I hope

00:18:52.890 --> 00:18:54.050 line:80%
you can do the same.

00:18:54.810 --> 00:18:55.850 line:80%
Stand for justice

00:18:56.130 --> 00:18:57.370 line:80%
in the martial world,

00:18:57.570 --> 00:18:58.862 line:80%
act chivalrously,

00:18:58.873 --> 00:19:00.319 line:80%
oppose the strong, and aid the weak,

00:19:00.330 --> 00:19:02.180 line:80%
so that grievances are addressed,

00:19:02.180 --> 00:19:04.130 line:80%
and everyone can achieve something.

00:19:29.780 --> 00:19:30.620 line:80%
(Trace Butterflies.)

00:19:56.610 --> 00:19:57.450 line:80%
Zhao, you're back.

00:19:58.220 --> 00:19:59.890 line:80%
(He lured the butterflies here?)

00:20:27.660 --> 00:20:28.850 line:80%
Ning, why are you here,

00:20:29.810 --> 00:20:32.420 line:80%
and why did you attract
so many Trace Butterflies?

00:20:32.740 --> 00:20:33.740 line:80%
Father has regretted

00:20:34.506 --> 00:20:35.886 line:80%
that during the Battle of Mount Tu,

00:20:36.370 --> 00:20:37.330 line:80%
he was a step too late

00:20:38.260 --> 00:20:39.850 line:80%
and could not fight with Ms. Cai.

00:20:41.420 --> 00:20:43.660 line:80%
Over the years, he tried many ways

00:20:44.220 --> 00:20:46.130 line:80%
and finally found Qiong pollen

00:20:46.330 --> 00:20:47.370 line:80%
to attract the butterflies,

00:20:48.690 --> 00:20:49.923 line:80%
but Ms. Cai had already passed.

00:20:54.980 --> 00:20:55.820 line:80%
This is for you.

00:21:01.640 --> 00:21:07.190 line:80%
♪But I can't forget your face♪

00:21:07.730 --> 00:21:11.440 line:80%
♪Life♪

00:21:11.450 --> 00:21:13.870 line:80%
♪Passes swiftly♪

00:21:14.660 --> 00:21:16.550 line:80%
♪Time is long♪

00:21:16.560 --> 00:21:18.300 line:80%
♪Pleasures are few♪

00:21:19.330 --> 00:21:21.260 line:80%
You deliberately mention my aunt today,

00:21:21.660 --> 00:21:22.740 line:80%
risking offending Lady Yin,

00:21:23.090 --> 00:21:24.180 line:80%
to stir conflict between us.

00:21:24.980 --> 00:21:26.530 line:80%
Now, you use these butterflies

00:21:26.530 --> 00:21:27.850 line:80%
to make me recall past emotions.

00:21:28.740 --> 00:21:29.810 line:80%
What exactly do you want?

00:21:30.180 --> 00:21:31.610 line:80%
♪In the end♪

00:21:32.220 --> 00:21:34.420 line:80%
I can't tell
if those around me are good.

00:21:36.050 --> 00:21:37.020 line:80%
I only trust you.

00:21:39.050 --> 00:21:40.420 line:80%
I want to remind you

00:21:41.460 --> 00:21:42.850 line:80%
not to easily trust others.

00:21:43.380 --> 00:21:44.730 line:80%
♪Liquor is strong♪

00:21:44.740 --> 00:21:46.940 line:80%
I also hope you'll protect me

00:21:47.570 --> 00:21:48.850 line:80%
for the sake of the bond

00:21:49.353 --> 00:21:50.546 line:80%
between Ms. Cai and my father.

00:21:52.850 --> 00:21:54.660 line:80%
How do you want me to protect you?

00:21:57.140 --> 00:22:00.630 line:80%
♪Leaving only me♪

00:22:01.290 --> 00:22:02.810 line:80%
I'm still poisoned.

00:22:03.420 --> 00:22:05.780 line:80%
Uncle Lei told me to go
to recover at Herb Hut.

00:22:06.370 --> 00:22:07.500 line:80%
I wonder

00:22:07.890 --> 00:22:08.810 line:80%
if you'd accompany me.

00:22:11.130 --> 00:22:11.970 line:80%
(Uncle Lei?)

00:22:16.020 --> 00:22:17.460 line:80%
Lei Xiuming

00:22:17.460 --> 00:22:19.290 line:80%
is praised by thousands.

00:22:19.940 --> 00:22:21.610 line:80%
He's the most beautiful man

00:22:21.610 --> 00:22:23.290 line:80%
in Jianghu.

00:22:23.290 --> 00:22:24.260 line:80%
(Herb Hut)

00:22:24.260 --> 00:22:25.530 line:80%
Pink in spring,

00:22:25.780 --> 00:22:27.260 line:80%
blue in summer,

00:22:27.740 --> 00:22:29.290 line:80%
yellow in autumn,

00:22:29.290 --> 00:22:30.660 line:80%
and white in winter.

00:22:30.660 --> 00:22:33.260 line:80%
He dresses better than the girls.

00:22:48.940 --> 00:22:50.500 line:80%
(Lei Xiuming, Qingque Sect)

00:22:50.500 --> 00:22:51.980 line:80%
I must look differently

00:22:52.073 --> 00:22:53.046 line:80%
from what your aunt said.

00:22:54.290 --> 00:22:55.940 line:80%
She rarely mentioned Qingque Sect

00:22:56.500 --> 00:22:58.020 line:80%
but often spoke of you

00:22:58.330 --> 00:22:59.740 line:80%
and Uncle Guo.

00:23:00.130 --> 00:23:00.970 line:80%
They're gone.

00:23:03.980 --> 00:23:05.220 line:80%
Only I, an invalid,

00:23:06.530 --> 00:23:07.420 line:80%
struggle to survive.

00:23:08.260 --> 00:23:09.180 line:80%
Past events

00:23:09.756 --> 00:23:10.910 line:80%
are better left unmentioned.

00:23:14.290 --> 00:23:16.500 line:80%
Uncle Lei, you are in the top three

00:23:16.500 --> 00:23:17.890 line:80%
on the Celebrity List.

00:23:18.980 --> 00:23:20.890 line:80%
They say you are

00:23:21.020 --> 00:23:22.090 line:80%
the greatest healer.

00:23:22.370 --> 00:23:24.500 line:80%
All heroes respect you.

00:23:32.220 --> 00:23:33.060 line:80%
Master.

00:23:34.050 --> 00:23:35.420 line:80%
Xingjia is ready.

00:23:35.890 --> 00:23:36.730 line:80%
Let's go.

00:23:41.460 --> 00:23:42.420 line:80%
Jueyinshu acupoint,

00:23:42.760 --> 00:23:43.630 line:80%
half a cun.

00:23:43.660 --> 00:23:44.500 line:80%
Uncle Lei,

00:23:45.180 --> 00:23:46.570 line:80%
that is a fatal acupoint.

00:23:47.220 --> 00:23:48.180 line:80%
Seeking life in death.

00:23:48.660 --> 00:23:49.660 line:80%
A risky medical move.

00:23:50.260 --> 00:23:51.100 line:80%
Uncle Lei, brilliant.

00:23:58.330 --> 00:23:59.170 line:80%
Zhao.

00:24:08.050 --> 00:24:08.890 line:80%
Ning,

00:24:09.530 --> 00:24:10.980 line:80%
I'm just an amateur.

00:24:11.370 --> 00:24:12.420 line:80%
If I make a mistake,

00:24:13.180 --> 00:24:14.220 line:80%
don't blame me.

00:24:14.610 --> 00:24:15.450 line:80%
It's fine.

00:24:16.130 --> 00:24:17.220 line:80%
Only half a life at risk.

00:24:18.460 --> 00:24:19.300 line:80%
Zhao,

00:24:19.850 --> 00:24:20.690 line:80%
don't worry.

00:24:41.130 --> 00:24:42.780 line:80%
(Irregular pulse.)

00:24:43.050 --> 00:24:44.370 line:80%
(Hidden old poison.)

00:24:51.810 --> 00:24:54.090 line:80%
You risked your life
on the cliff to protect me

00:24:54.940 --> 00:24:56.220 line:80%
and helped remove my poison.

00:24:57.090 --> 00:24:57.930 line:80%
I'm truly grateful.

00:25:00.460 --> 00:25:02.570 line:80%
I heard you were sickly as a child.

00:25:03.290 --> 00:25:04.700 line:80%
Uncle Chang took great care,

00:25:05.020 --> 00:25:06.610 line:80%
so you never left Chang Fort.

00:25:07.492 --> 00:25:08.846 line:80%
But that night, during the attack,

00:25:09.420 --> 00:25:11.220 line:80%
I saw your agile moves.

00:25:11.610 --> 00:25:12.940 line:80%
During the acupuncture session,

00:25:13.050 --> 00:25:14.780 line:80%
I sensed your immense

00:25:15.220 --> 00:25:16.406 line:80%
and extraordinary inner power.

00:25:18.700 --> 00:25:19.890 line:80%
Since I recovered at ten,

00:25:21.169 --> 00:25:22.975 line:80%
my father often passed on
inner power to me.

00:25:23.780 --> 00:25:24.850 line:80%
Uncles in the fort

00:25:25.166 --> 00:25:26.612 line:80%
also taught me everything they knew.

00:25:28.330 --> 00:25:30.020 line:80%
You have such skill

00:25:30.020 --> 00:25:31.260 line:80%
before reaching adulthood.

00:25:31.700 --> 00:25:33.130 line:80%
How gifted.

00:25:33.980 --> 00:25:35.086 line:80%
What about this old poison?

00:25:36.130 --> 00:25:37.130 line:80%
Where did it come from?

00:25:39.130 --> 00:25:40.290 line:80%
I was weak since childhood.

00:25:41.810 --> 00:25:44.130 line:80%
My father once used
a counter-poison method

00:25:45.890 --> 00:25:47.020 line:80%
to help me survive.

00:25:47.940 --> 00:25:50.220 line:80%
If it can ease your doubts,

00:25:51.460 --> 00:25:53.180 line:80%
I can write the formula for you.

00:26:20.050 --> 00:26:21.570 line:80%
Ning, how do you feel?

00:26:25.530 --> 00:26:26.370 line:80%
Let's go back.

00:26:35.290 --> 00:26:36.130 line:80%
Zhao,

00:26:36.460 --> 00:26:38.130 line:80%
there seems to be poison in the water.

00:26:43.570 --> 00:26:44.530 line:80%
Chang Ning!

00:27:07.130 --> 00:27:08.260 line:80%
Zhao, what's wrong?

00:27:10.810 --> 00:27:12.260 line:80%
You're fair-skinned and handsome,

00:27:13.050 --> 00:27:14.330 line:80%
refined and noble,

00:27:15.220 --> 00:27:16.940 line:80%
nothing like Uncle Chang.

00:27:19.370 --> 00:27:20.260 line:80%
Zhao,

00:27:21.570 --> 00:27:22.740 line:80%
have you ever seen my mother?

00:28:01.020 --> 00:28:01.860 line:80%
Take medicine.

00:28:13.530 --> 00:28:14.370 line:80%
What's this?

00:28:15.330 --> 00:28:16.170 line:80%
Smiley.

00:28:16.610 --> 00:28:17.610 line:80%
My aunt taught me,

00:28:17.890 --> 00:28:18.980 line:80%
hoping whoever eats it

00:28:19.330 --> 00:28:20.460 line:80%
will be happy.

00:28:31.130 --> 00:28:31.970 line:80%
So sweet.

00:28:36.660 --> 00:28:38.020 line:80%
Since you are fine now,

00:28:39.660 --> 00:28:40.500 line:80%
please go back.

00:28:43.980 --> 00:28:44.820 line:80%
Zhao,

00:28:45.780 --> 00:28:47.290 line:80%
may I stay for a few days?

00:28:47.810 --> 00:28:48.890 line:80%
When my wounds heal,

00:28:49.327 --> 00:28:50.487 line:80%
I'll return to Peace Chamber.

00:28:53.290 --> 00:28:54.500 line:80%
My poison isn't cleared;

00:28:56.290 --> 00:28:58.260 line:80%
someone tampered with the herbal bath.

00:28:59.020 --> 00:29:00.780 line:80%
You can't just watch me die.

00:29:31.850 --> 00:29:32.850 line:80%
My purple jade inkstone!

00:29:32.980 --> 00:29:33.980 line:80%
Don't come near me.

00:29:34.260 --> 00:29:35.370 line:80%
I'll kill you.

00:29:35.530 --> 00:29:37.090 line:80%
The effect is so strong?

00:29:37.570 --> 00:29:38.570 line:80%
You are a murderer!

00:29:38.570 --> 00:29:39.410 line:80%
Oh, my goodness.

00:29:40.050 --> 00:29:42.090 line:80%
I only added a little Truth Teller
in the medicine.

00:29:43.940 --> 00:29:44.810 line:80%
Die!

00:29:46.740 --> 00:29:47.580 line:80%
Chang Ning.

00:29:47.740 --> 00:29:48.580 line:80%
Chang Ning,

00:29:48.590 --> 00:29:49.430 line:80%
wake up!

00:29:49.440 --> 00:29:50.320 line:80%
Don't come near.

00:29:50.500 --> 00:29:51.610 line:80%
You killed my father!

00:29:51.940 --> 00:29:53.420 line:80%
You killed my father!

00:29:54.740 --> 00:29:56.050 line:80%
He really is Uncle Chang's son.

00:29:56.090 --> 00:29:56.940 line:80%
I'll kill you!

00:29:57.020 --> 00:29:58.410 line:80%
Chang Ning, wake up!

00:30:00.130 --> 00:30:01.090 line:80%
You killed my father!

00:30:01.610 --> 00:30:02.660 line:80%
I'll kill you!

00:30:03.740 --> 00:30:04.660 line:80%
I'll kill you!

00:30:07.050 --> 00:30:07.890 line:80%
Oh, no.

00:30:07.920 --> 00:30:09.160 line:80%
He really thinks I'm his enemy.

00:30:13.020 --> 00:30:13.860 line:80%
Have you heard?

00:30:14.330 --> 00:30:16.020 line:80%
Chang Ning moved into Chunling Cottage.

00:30:16.130 --> 00:30:17.660 line:80%
They're living together.

00:30:18.050 --> 00:30:19.220 line:80%
How improper!

00:30:20.500 --> 00:30:21.340 line:80%
Zhao, be careful.

00:30:40.940 --> 00:30:42.500 line:80%
- Let's go.
- Go!

00:30:43.380 --> 00:30:45.260 line:80%
(Glow of Moonlight and Flowers)

00:30:47.613 --> 00:30:48.813 line:80%
Osmanthus and angelica congee.

00:30:49.090 --> 00:30:50.363 line:80%
It calms the mind, regulates qi,

00:30:50.810 --> 00:30:51.740 line:80%
and helps

00:30:51.740 --> 00:30:52.610 line:80%
with staying up late

00:30:53.050 --> 00:30:53.890 line:80%
and headaches.

00:30:58.090 --> 00:30:59.570 line:80%
Last night, I sleepwalked.

00:31:00.180 --> 00:31:01.290 line:80%
I hope I didn't break

00:31:01.290 --> 00:31:02.570 line:80%
anything of yours.

00:31:04.420 --> 00:31:05.500 line:80%
It's fine.

00:31:05.740 --> 00:31:07.210 line:80%
It's understandable for sleepwalking.

00:31:07.570 --> 00:31:08.410 line:80%
I won't mind.

00:31:09.890 --> 00:31:11.810 line:80%
You helped me several times,

00:31:12.890 --> 00:31:13.850 line:80%
gave me sweet congee,

00:31:14.500 --> 00:31:15.573 line:80%
and generously let me stay.

00:31:16.290 --> 00:31:17.436 line:80%
I must reward you handsomely.

00:31:20.620 --> 00:31:21.470 line:80%
Ning,

00:31:21.500 --> 00:31:22.890 line:80%
are you rich?

00:31:24.049 --> 00:31:25.295 line:80%
Father had considerable savings.

00:31:25.570 --> 00:31:26.850 line:80%
Not many rare medicine formulas.

00:31:27.460 --> 00:31:30.370 line:80%
But treasures and money

00:31:30.740 --> 00:31:32.570 line:80%
are hidden in places that only I know.

00:31:32.980 --> 00:31:34.260 line:80%
So, you are rich.

00:31:34.780 --> 00:31:35.620 line:80%
Not really.

00:31:36.780 --> 00:31:38.090 line:80%
But if you protect me

00:31:38.570 --> 00:31:40.290 line:80%
in Qingque Sect,

00:31:40.703 --> 00:31:41.896 line:80%
after going down the mountain,

00:31:42.530 --> 00:31:43.923 line:80%
I'm willing to give all my wealth.

00:31:45.220 --> 00:31:46.060 line:80%
All of it?

00:31:46.500 --> 00:31:47.340 line:80%
Yes.

00:31:47.610 --> 00:31:48.450 line:80%
A gentleman's word?

00:31:48.740 --> 00:31:49.580 line:80%
Hard to retract.

00:31:49.780 --> 00:31:50.620 line:80%
Then it's settled.

00:31:50.810 --> 00:31:51.850 line:80%
I'll protect you.

00:31:52.020 --> 00:31:53.150 line:80%
- Eat up.
- Thanks.

00:32:02.926 --> 00:32:03.992 line:80%
Your gesture is wrong here.

00:32:04.260 --> 00:32:05.260 line:80%
Bend it more,

00:32:06.370 --> 00:32:07.220 line:80%
open this side,

00:32:08.610 --> 00:32:09.776 line:80%
and apply force in your palm.

00:32:11.313 --> 00:32:12.689 line:80%
The mindful way of Luoying Valley

00:32:12.700 --> 00:32:14.330 line:80%
will help your wound heal sooner.

00:32:14.940 --> 00:32:16.060 line:80%
I was sickly in childhood.

00:32:16.130 --> 00:32:16.980 line:80%
It also helped me.

00:32:17.660 --> 00:32:19.070 line:80%
- Again.
- Okay.

00:32:19.090 --> 00:32:20.370 line:80%
Living in the same chamber,

00:32:20.370 --> 00:32:21.980 line:80%
young and affectionate.

00:32:22.260 --> 00:32:23.610 line:80%
How friendly.

00:32:24.330 --> 00:32:26.850 line:80%
Why are you two here?

00:32:27.050 --> 00:32:29.740 line:80%
Chang has moved here.

00:32:30.180 --> 00:32:31.020 line:80%
Why?

00:32:31.330 --> 00:32:32.500 line:80%
Can't we come?

00:32:45.780 --> 00:32:46.660 line:80%
Just so-so.

00:32:47.420 --> 00:32:48.330 line:80%
I heard

00:32:49.180 --> 00:32:50.330 line:80%
that last night,

00:32:50.500 --> 00:32:51.850 line:80%
you and he

00:32:52.330 --> 00:32:53.180 line:80%
were quite noisy.

00:32:54.370 --> 00:32:55.890 line:80%
Noisy?

00:32:57.610 --> 00:32:58.530 line:80%
More than that.

00:32:59.610 --> 00:33:01.850 line:80%
We were earth-shattering.

00:33:03.020 --> 00:33:06.130 line:80%
My sister and Ning were sparring.

00:33:06.130 --> 00:33:07.780 line:80%
Sparring?

00:33:09.420 --> 00:33:10.260 line:80%
Zhao,

00:33:10.700 --> 00:33:12.290 line:80%
if others hear that you

00:33:12.740 --> 00:33:13.850 line:80%
spent the night together,

00:33:14.130 --> 00:33:15.530 line:80%
it will spread rumors.

00:33:17.260 --> 00:33:19.500 line:80%
Let it spread.

00:33:19.810 --> 00:33:22.190 line:80%
It won't cost me any money, right?

00:33:22.220 --> 00:33:23.180 line:80%
No.

00:33:23.570 --> 00:33:25.090 line:80%
What on earth are you two up to?

00:33:25.370 --> 00:33:26.700 line:80%
That's our secret.

00:33:27.420 --> 00:33:28.940 line:80%
We can't tell you.

00:33:29.740 --> 00:33:30.980 line:80%
It's already autumn.

00:33:35.090 --> 00:33:37.050 line:80%
Why are toads still croaking?

00:33:39.660 --> 00:33:40.456 line:80%
Ning,

00:33:40.467 --> 00:33:41.810 line:80%
your injuries haven't healed yet.

00:33:42.610 --> 00:33:43.850 line:80%
Let's rest first.

00:33:46.260 --> 00:33:47.330 line:80%
Stop right there!

00:33:48.530 --> 00:33:49.700 line:80%
- Lingbo.
- What?

00:33:49.890 --> 00:33:50.940 line:80%
Master repeatedly said

00:33:51.090 --> 00:33:52.260 line:80%
no more conflicts with them.

00:33:52.700 --> 00:33:55.050 line:80%
Ribbit, ribbit, ribbit.

00:33:55.850 --> 00:33:57.370 line:80%
I'm too lazy to argue with them.

00:33:58.330 --> 00:33:59.170 line:80%
Lingbo.

00:34:00.220 --> 00:34:01.420 line:80%
Didn't you say

00:34:02.050 --> 00:34:03.076 line:80%
that peace brings wealth?

00:34:03.940 --> 00:34:04.890 line:80%
Why provoke her?

00:34:04.890 --> 00:34:05.940 line:80%
I don't want trouble,

00:34:06.773 --> 00:34:08.033 line:80%
but I'm not afraid of it either.

00:34:08.490 --> 00:34:10.220 line:80%
For those who stir conflict,

00:34:10.450 --> 00:34:11.540 line:80%
you must not indulge them.

00:34:16.620 --> 00:34:18.660 line:80%
This is family heritage.

00:34:19.540 --> 00:34:21.740 line:80%
Her grandfather, Yin Dai,
relied on words alone

00:34:22.260 --> 00:34:25.010 line:80%
to send your aunt to kill the demon.

00:34:25.490 --> 00:34:27.740 line:80%
Why are you sowing discord again?

00:34:30.140 --> 00:34:31.220 line:80%
To approach me,

00:34:31.740 --> 00:34:33.930 line:80%
you even tampered with the herbal bath

00:34:34.220 --> 00:34:35.660 line:80%
and moved here.

00:34:36.890 --> 00:34:37.930 line:80%
What exactly do you want?

00:34:38.330 --> 00:34:39.170 line:80%
Or,

00:34:40.220 --> 00:34:41.273 line:80%
what do you want me to do?

00:34:45.100 --> 00:34:46.490 line:80%
You're truly clever.

00:34:47.780 --> 00:34:49.010 line:80%
I did all this

00:34:49.660 --> 00:34:51.580 line:80%
just to show you the truth.

00:34:52.620 --> 00:34:54.260 line:80%
The one who pushed your aunt

00:34:54.780 --> 00:34:56.450 line:80%
to kill the demon alone

00:34:56.780 --> 00:34:57.890 line:80%
was Lord Yin.

00:34:58.810 --> 00:35:00.220 line:80%
If you don't believe me,

00:35:00.540 --> 00:35:02.450 line:80%
you can check the secret room
in the Library.

00:35:03.100 --> 00:35:04.220 line:80%
I heard

00:35:04.850 --> 00:35:07.100 line:80%
every lord has a handbook.

00:35:08.140 --> 00:35:09.620 line:80%
There must be

00:35:09.620 --> 00:35:10.810 line:80%
some clues in it.

00:35:11.410 --> 00:35:12.260 line:80%
Library?

00:35:20.020 --> 00:35:23.620 line:80%
(Library)

00:35:41.740 --> 00:35:42.850 line:80%
Xuanji Array.

00:36:03.780 --> 00:36:06.900 line:80%
(Pillar of Righteousness)

00:36:31.540 --> 00:36:32.380 line:80%
(6th)

00:36:32.380 --> 00:36:35.260 line:80%
(11th)
(Master is the 20th lord.)

00:36:36.100 --> 00:36:38.620 line:80%
(18th)
(Yin Dai should be the 19th.)

00:36:52.970 --> 00:36:54.140 line:80%
Ning?

00:36:55.970 --> 00:36:57.140 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:36:57.450 --> 00:36:58.290 line:80%
To return the favor,

00:36:59.180 --> 00:37:00.330 line:80%
I'm here to search

00:37:00.740 --> 00:37:01.660 line:80%
for the truth with you.

00:37:07.121 --> 00:37:17.781 line:80%
=Generation to Generation=

00:37:36.541 --> 00:37:40.951 line:80%
♪The breeze is gentle,
and spring is fair♪

00:37:41.516 --> 00:37:46.131 line:80%
♪I roam the rivers and hills
in the martial world♪

00:37:46.471 --> 00:37:51.036 line:80%
♪With a shining cup,
I drink with delight tonight♪

00:37:51.561 --> 00:37:55.861 line:80%
♪Free to wander in the world♪

00:37:58.806 --> 00:38:03.506 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:04.031 --> 00:38:08.321 line:80%
♪I rest beneath the stars' soft gleam♪

00:38:08.981 --> 00:38:13.011 line:80%
♪The night is calm, still as a stream♪

00:38:13.326 --> 00:38:18.451 line:80%
♪It washes away all judgment and scheme♪

00:38:19.026 --> 00:38:23.836 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:38:24.051 --> 00:38:28.221 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:38:28.946 --> 00:38:32.881 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:38:33.381 --> 00:38:38.656 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪

00:39:01.386 --> 00:39:06.516 line:80%
♪I drink with the breeze,
lost in my dreams♪

00:39:06.881 --> 00:39:11.251 line:80%
♪I hold the bright moon
as I return home♪

00:39:11.516 --> 00:39:15.646 line:80%
♪I freely roam in the world♪

00:39:15.831 --> 00:39:21.406 line:80%
♪All I ask is that you go with me♪